These applescripts are provided as-is and with absolutely no warranties. The
application and application bundle are all editable, and were created with
Script Editor.


== Installation: ==

Copy "Automount secure drive Folder Action.scpt" to
/Library/Scripts/Folder Action Scripts/, and attach it as a folder action to
/Volumes/


== Setup: ==

Insert the memory stick you wish to use, and drag the mounted volume from the
desktop onto the "Prepare secure drive droplet" application bundle


== Restoring: ==

Insert the 'secure' memory stick, select 'cancel' when prompted for the
password, and run the "Restore secure drive" application.
